\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 In a world where you can find a drug, food, chemical, etc to make you feel better whenever you feel bad\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 In a culture that does everything to avoid feeling not only physical pain but also emotional pain\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 In a place where we're so scared our kids won't be able to handle a loss at the age of 7 so we give everyone participation trophies...\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 Is it any wonder we can't handle suffering.\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 We run from it at all costs...and it shows in our world.\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 But Paul is giving us a different perspective...a different way to live life\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl0\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 I told you at the beginning of the series that I would be challenging your faith and and today is one of those to help reveal...not replace or lose but to reveal whether you are really saved or not.\'a0 \cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 It is easy to pray a prayer and not really mean what you say\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 It is easy to show up to church\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 It is hard to suffer for other and Christ. \cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 The reality is we all suffer but we have to suffer for the right reasons....\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 Is it Satan or Stupid or Sanctification (not sure I want to out this here????)\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec5 ?????\cf2 \strokec2 \uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\cf5 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
